text: "Oceans" is a 1992 song by alternative rock band Pearl Jam and is the fourth and final single from their debut studio album Ten. It wasn't released as a single in the United States until 1995 and went to number 16 in New Zealand, number 30 in the Netherlands and number 35 in Belgium. == References == Category:1992 songs Category:Rock songs Category:Pearl Jam songs Category:Alternative rock songs
